    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom-quality shine, and the interior remains in pristine, factory-fresh condition with no signs of wear. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, providing a smooth and powerful driving experience that truly reflects the car's well-maintained history.",
